data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath home features a tri-level floor plan with living room, dining room and kitchen on the main level, main bedroom, bath and 2 other bedrooms on the upper level and family room with fireplace, 1 bedroom and bath as well as laundry closet on the lower level.  There is no HOA.   This home is being sold "as is" with no repairs. Home is unfurnished.   New boiler installed in 2008 and evaporative cooler in 2022.   All information, including measurements and square feet, deemed reliable but not guaranteed and should be verified by Buyer(s).
